title: Dishwasher Drain Solenoid and Bracket Assembly
description: Dishwasher Drain Solenoid and Bracket Assembly ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 11 Reviews PartSelect Number PS1481923 Manufacturer Part Number WD21X10268 This valve opens in order for the water to drain out of the dishwasher.

installationInstructions.author: Hector from West Melbourne, FL
installationInstructions.title: Dishwasher water will not drain.
installationInstructions.content: Very easy about 5 min replacement, Checked electrical conductivity to verify I had a bad solinoid, after I received the new part. I removed and replaced part by only removing  and re-installed  2 screws and spring. Dishwasher worked like new.
